'''Lindiwe Chibi''' (1976–2007), yari umukinnyi wa filime wo [[Afurika y’Epfo|muri Afrika yepfo]] . Babona ari kimwe mu film karuhariwe mu televiziyo [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika y'Epfo]], <ref name="markettheatre">https://markettheatre.co.za/2018/08/03/lindiwe-chibi-memorialised-at-the-market-square/</ref> arimo izwi uruhare 'Doobsie' mu ikundwa serial ''Muvhango.'' <ref>https://esat.sun.ac.za/index.php/Lindiwe_Chibi</ref>

== Amasasu n'urupfu ==
Ku ya 30 Mata 2005, umukunzi we Dan Mokoena, yamurashe mu maso igihe Chibi yari kwa nyina. <ref name="dob">https://www.news24.com/news24/doobsie-written-out-of-soapie-20070510</ref> Amasasu yarashwe hafi, yinjira mu itama asohoka inyuma y'umutwe. Yahise ajyanwa mu bitaro bya Garden  Clinic, amara ibyumweru bitatu muri koma. Amaze guhaguruka ava muri koma, yamugaye iburyo bw'umubiri we. <ref name="IOL">https://www.iol.co.za/news/south-africa/actress-lindiwe-chibi-dies-352341</ref> Igihe yari amaze gukira ibikomere byica, yapfuye azize umusonga mu bitaro bya Chris Hani-Baragwanath i Soweto mu 2007 afite imyaka 31. <ref>https://www.all4women.co.za/689929/entertainment/celebrity-photo-galleries/gallery-soapie-stars-who-died-in-real-life/4</ref>

== Umwuga ==
Mu 1995, yatangiye umwuga wo gukina umwuga wo gukina ikinamico ''Ekuseni yakinwaga'' kuri Civic Theatre. Hanyuma yakinnye ''Game wo'' gukina kuri Windybrow Theatre, aho yakiriye igihembo cyumukinnyi mwiza. Hanyuma yakinnye nka 'Stella Kowalski' mumikino gakondo, ''A Street Car'' Yitwa Desire ndetse no muri ''The Pen na Molora'' . <ref name="IOL" /> Yakoze umugizi wa nabi uzwi cyane 'Doobsie' muri serivise ya televiziyo ''Muvhango'' . <ref>https://www.news24.com/news24/stars-shooting-an-accident-20050518</ref> Nyuma y'urupfu rwe, uruhare rwe rwatangajwe ko yeguye. <ref name="dob" />

Ku ya 3 Kanama 2018, Isoko rya Theatre Foundation ryiswe icyumba cyo hejuru cyo mu cyubahiro cya Chibi. <ref name="markettheatre" />

